{"tid":876921,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"普通經濟題 [Keynesian]","createTime":"2018-10-26T03:28:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-26T11:47:35.000Z","uid":71237,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"924bb6c40c662c311d30bd6e0afbdb9de50eb1df","tid":876921,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T03:28:48.000Z","msg":"題型係以前AL年代學校mock exam嘅題目，啲數字就係我專登set嘅。<br />\n大學學過Keynesian model的同學都可以嚟試下。<br />\n<br />\nC = 1600 + 0.8Yd<br />\nI = 1000<br />\nG = 900<br />\n<br />\nYd = Y - T<br />\nT = 0.35C<br />\n<br />\nFind the value of Y at equilibrium."},{"pid":"ba910ce26850c6bfaddeabac5ce45b7f2e6ac87d","tid":876921,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T07:26:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68371f705d5e94fc45b200732104ff796a45d65a","tid":876921,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T09:03:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b4cbb6f36aa367065671dbbe181acba30b9ded5","tid":876921,"uid":11553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T09:46:14.000Z","msg":"9025<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1eaed7cf30a8a959ce84810c917d43dfa4a04a56","tid":876921,"uid":11553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b4cbb6f36aa367065671dbbe181acba30b9ded5","tid":876921,"uid":11553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T09:46:14.000Z","msg":"9025<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T09:52:57.000Z","msg":"sor 好似係 8400<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37a8d687a98638934ea1a68f1a62adbc177be2f5","tid":876921,"uid":71237,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1eaed7cf30a8a959ce84810c917d43dfa4a04a56","tid":876921,"uid":11553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b4cbb6f36aa367065671dbbe181acba30b9ded5","tid":876921,"uid":11553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T09:46:14.000Z","msg":"9025<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T09:52:57.000Z","msg":"sor 好似係 8400<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T09:59:01.000Z","msg":"正確。<br />\n依種consumption tax的題目即使喺大學書都比較少見。<br />\n<br />\n我的做法：<br />\nC = 1600 + 0.8(Y - 0.35C)<br />\nC = 1600 + 0.8Y - 0.28C<br />\n1.28C = 1600 + 0.8Y<br />\nC = 1250 + 0.625Y<br />\n<br />\nAt equilibrium, Y = C + I + G<br />\nY = 1250 + 0.625Y + 1000 + 900<br />\nY = 3150 + 0.625Y<br />\n0.375Y = 3150<br />\nY = 8400"},{"pid":"4ed2501a0e423e80b7db9a5c8858e5eeca8b3f38","tid":876921,"uid":11553,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"37a8d687a98638934ea1a68f1a62adbc177be2f5","tid":876921,"uid":71237,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1eaed7cf30a8a959ce84810c917d43dfa4a04a56","tid":876921,"uid":11553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b4cbb6f36aa367065671dbbe181acba30b9ded5","tid":876921,"uid":11553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T09:46:14.000Z","msg":"9025<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T09:52:57.000Z","msg":"sor 好似係 8400<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T09:59:01.000Z","msg":"正確。<br />\n依種consumption tax的題目即使喺大學書都比較少見。<br />\n<br />\n我的做法：<br />\nC = 1600 + 0.8(Y - 0.35C)<br />\nC = 1600 + 0.8Y - 0.28C<br />\n1.28C = 1600 + 0.8Y<br />\nC = 1250 + 0.625Y<br />\n<br />\nAt equilibrium, Y = C + I + G<br />\nY = 1250 + 0.625Y + 1000 + 900<br />\nY = 3150 + 0.625Y<br />\n0.375Y = 3150<br />\nY = 8400"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T10:19:43.000Z","msg":"返工悶悶地做<br />\n同樣方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果返工好似做Econ題目咁有model就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nAL econ A + UG econ major<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eded870b12a41e622434f81d1f25529fe72212a","tid":876921,"uid":71237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T10:34:54.000Z","msg":"下一題：<br />\n依題我以前year 1研究balanced budget multiplier果陣發現嘅。<br />\n當income tax rate符合某個條件，增加G係唔會影響fiscal balance。<br />\n<br />\nC = 100 + 0.75Yd<br />\nI = 100 + 0.15Y<br />\nG = G* = 100<br />\n<br />\nYd = Y - T<br />\nT = tY<br />\n<br />\nQ1. Express the expenditure multiplier in terms of t.<br />\n<br />\nQ2. Find the income tax rate (t) such any increase in autonomous government expenditure (G*) would have no effect on the fiscal balance (T - G)."},{"pid":"1204257f2f6d7ef991b60ea02f335a00214f023a","tid":876921,"uid":29929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T10:48:07.000Z","msg":"好有大雞影子<br />\n<br />\n如果大雞似你有番咁上下能力 高登連登莘莘學子就有福"},{"pid":"ef3205dee0d450eea9aedc9570e03957c4362a51","tid":876921,"uid":71237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1204257f2f6d7ef991b60ea02f335a00214f023a","tid":876921,"uid":29929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T10:48:07.000Z","msg":"好有大雞影子<br />\n<br />\n如果大雞似你有番咁上下能力 高登連登莘莘學子就有福"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T10:59:30.000Z","msg":"我個標題抄佢先有佢影子者 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c90eca095b0914cff4f742dbd4cf2bae0232754","tid":876921,"uid":165028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T11:35:24.000Z","msg":"可唔可以搵d 時間講下micro<br />\n真心想學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"264ed49765928a0d58897c2e0cf874962eef599d","tid":876921,"uid":1788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6eded870b12a41e622434f81d1f25529fe72212a","tid":876921,"uid":71237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T10:34:54.000Z","msg":"下一題：<br />\n依題我以前year 1研究balanced budget multiplier果陣發現嘅。<br />\n當income tax rate符合某個條件，增加G係唔會影響fiscal balance。<br />\n<br />\nC = 100 + 0.75Yd<br />\nI = 100 + 0.15Y<br />\nG = G* = 100<br />\n<br />\nYd = Y - T<br />\nT = tY<br />\n<br />\nQ1. Express the expenditure multiplier in terms of t.<br />\n<br />\nQ2. Find the income tax rate (t) such any increase in autonomous government expenditure (G*) would have no effect on the fiscal balance (T - G)."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T11:47:35.000Z","msg":"Q1:<br />\nMultiplier=1/(0.1+0.75t)<br />\n<br />\nQ2:<br />\nChange in G = Change in T<br />\nG&rsquo;-G=t((G&rsquo;-G)/(0.1+0.75t))<br />\n1=t/(0.1+0.75t)<br />\nt=0.1+0.75t<br />\nt=0.4=40%"}]}